From dc9d1791ddfbbd6dfa5af4fd9c3d78ce188b9b66 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 04:20:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add real research citations and Sources sections to 18 legacy
 blog posts

Follow-up to the earlier evidence-audit commit: brings every remaining blog
post that had zero citations up to the site's evidence-based house style
(inline "(Author et al., Year)" citations + a "Sources & Further Reading"
section with DOI/PubMed links), per the request that all articles be backed
by real research rather than unsourced opinion.

Files updated, each with a new Sources & Further Reading section and PubMed-
sourced inline citations woven into the existing body copy:
- best-time-to-start-laser-mumbai.html
- is-laser-hair-removal-permanent.html
- signs-laser-hair-removal-is-working.html
- laser-hair-removal-aftercare.html
- laser-hair-removal-vs-waxing.html (completes today's earlier partial fix)
- how-to-prepare-for-first-laser-hair-removal-session.html (completes today's
  earlier partial fix)
- laser-hair-removal-for-pcos.html (completes today's earlier partial fix)
- hifu-everything-you-need-to-know.html
- q-switched-laser-truth.html
- chemical-peels-for-indian-skin.html
- cryolipolysis-complete-guide.html
- fat-freeze-realistic-expectations.html
- cellulite-treatment-what-works.html
- monsoon-skincare-mumbai.html
- under-eye-dark-circles-treatments.html
- post-pregnancy-body-plan.html (completes today's earlier partial fix)
- understanding-melasma.html (completes today's earlier partial fix)
- when-indian-women-start-anti-ageing.html

Where a specific number/claim in the existing copy (e.g. "80-90% permanent
reduction", "40-60% stretch mark improvement", "SPF prevents 80% of ageing")
turned out not to be supported by real literature at that magnitude, the
claim was corrected to the actual figure found in the literature or hedged
appropriately rather than left as an invented citation. All JSON-LD blocks
validated as parseable JSON and all files checked for HTML well-formedness
after editing.
