+            <li id="src-2">Boey GE, Wasilenchuk JL. "Fat reduction in the inner thigh using a prototype cryolipolysis applicator." <em>Dermatologic Surgery</em>, 2014. — <a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/01.DSS.0000452628.99209.4f" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">source</a></li>
+            <li id="src-3">Zelickson BD, Burns AJ, Kilmer SL. "Cryolipolysis for safe and effective inner thigh fat reduction." <em>Lasers in Surgery and Medicine</em>, 2015. — <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/lsm.22320" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">source</a></li>
