+          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">Sources &amp; Further Reading</h2>
+          <ol style="font-size:0.92rem; color:var(--color-text-light,#574C3F); line-height:1.8; padding-left:1.25rem;">
+            <li id="src-1">Sarkar R, Ranjan R, Garg S, Garg VK, Sonthalia S, Bansal S. "Periorbital Hyperpigmentation: A Comprehensive Review." <em>The Journal of Clinical and Aesthetic Dermatology</em>, 2016. — <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC4756872/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">source</a></li>
+            <li id="src-2">Michelle L, Pouldar Foulad D, Ekelem C, Saedi N, Mesinkovska NA. "Treatments of Periorbital Hyperpigmentation: A Systematic Review." <em>Dermatologic Surgery</em>, 2021. — <a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/DSS.0000000000002484" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">source</a></li>
